{
  "id": "sotf-survival-of-the-fittest-001",
  "name": "Survival of the Fittest",
  "description": "Three Matrix hosts from the Shadowrun 3E adventure 'Survival of the Fittest'. Each host represents a distinct scenario — run them independently or as part of the full campaign.",
  "version": "1.0",
  "gmNotes": "Source: Survival of the Fittest (WizKids/FanPro, 2002). Three hosts across three adventures: Shasta Lodge Mainframe (The Lodge, p.30), Children of the Dragon Temple (Meet the New Boss, p.40), and Wuxing Skytower (Scaling the Dragon's Tower, p.76). The Wuxing host step numbers and exact rating were unrecoverable from the OCR scan — step values and UV rating are GM best-estimates based on IC escalation and context.",
  "hostGMNotes": {
    "host-sotf-shasta-lodge": "Adventure: The Lodge. Hestaby's dragon lair at Mt. Shasta. Decker goal: reach the Kallisti file (500 Mp, offline storage). The offline system has the SAME sheaf but shuts down at tally 20. Connecting the offline unit to the mainframe requires Computer (4) test (~1 minute). Access to the mainframe allows Control Slave (security cameras + maglocks). Shutdown at tally 43.",
    "host-sotf-shasta-offline": "Adventure: The Lodge. The isolated data storage where the Kallisti file is kept. Can only be accessed on-site OR if connected to the main Lodge Mainframe (Computer (4) test, ~1 minute). Same sheaf as the mainframe but shuts down at step 20 instead of 43. Contains Scramble IC-8 protecting the Kallisti file.",
    "host-sotf-children-dragon": "Adventure: Meet the New Boss (Denver, UCAS sector). Martin Goldwing's cult — Children of the Dragon, a Ghostwalker front. Morningstar's personal files and telecomm records (150 Mp) are the target — protected by Rating 5 Data Bomb. Files implicate Morningstar in working for Lofwyr, though a Computer (6) test reveals they were tampered with. Very long sheaf — this is a hardened system.",
    "host-sotf-wuxing-skytower": "Adventure: Scaling the Dragon's Tower (Hong Kong). Wuxing megacorp HQ. Decker goal: override elevator passcode OR suppress external camera alarms to let the team enter the penthouse. Control Slave = elevator, Edit Slave = suppress cameras/alarms. IMPORTANT: Step numbers approximate — source OCR was unrecoverable for this sheaf. UV rating estimated from IC power level (Killer-12, Crippler-10). Adjust to taste."
  },
  "createdAt": 1750000000000,
  "entryHostIds": [
    "host-sotf-shasta-lodge",
    "host-sotf-children-dragon",
    "host-sotf-wuxing-skytower"
  ],
